1. *Recimo* da će sutra biti lepo vreme. (Let's say that it will be nice weather tomorrow.)
2. On je rekao da je *recimo* odlučio da se preseli. (He said that he had, let's say, decided to move.)
3. *Recimo* da sam bio u pravu. (Let's say that I was right.)
4. Želeo bih da *recimo* nastavim da radim na ovom projektu. (I would like to, let's say, continue working on this project.)
5. *Recimo* da smo zaista znali istinu. (Let's say that we really knew the truth.)